<taxonomicName id="4C724D72FF9DFFD892F0EB7E14F4FAE3" authority="(Linnaeus 1753: 377) Irwin &amp; Barneby (1982: 252)" authorityName="Irwin &amp; Barneby" authorityPageNumber="252" authorityYear="1982" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityPageNumber="377" baseAuthorityYear="1753" box="[178,969,1291,1318]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Senna" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="27" pageNumber="272" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="obtusifolia">
