<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B00FF9DFFD8903EEB7E14F4FAE3" author="Irwin, H. S. &amp; Barneby, R. C." box="[636,969,1291,1318]" pageId="27" pageNumber="272" pagination="1 - 918" refId="ref21480" refString="Irwin, H. S. &amp; Barneby, R. C. (1982) The American Cassiinae: A synoptical revision of Leguminosae - Tribe Cassieae subtribe Cassiinae in the New World. Memoirs of the New York Botanical Garden 35: 1 - 918." type="journal article" year="1982">Irwin &amp; Barneby (1982: 252)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
